# HUD::SET_WAYPOINT_OFF

## Summary
Switches off the waypoint blip if it is active

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This native removes the current waypoint from the map.

Example:
C#:
Function.Call(Hash.SET_WAYPOINT_OFF);

C++:
HUD::SET_WAYPOINT_OFF();
